<p>quick aside - I'm pretty sure this design from 1992 inspired Yasuhiro Nightow's design for Legato Bluesummers in Trigun (1995).<br>
<br>
Nightow was on the same wavelength, at any rate. Also a figure/sculpture enthusiast! But that's another thread.</p>
